E4Plus1.uk.description: The Locomotion Interruption: Leonard and Amy take an impromptu road trip to Arizona to pick up Sheldon when his epic railway journey ends in chaos. Penny has an interview. (S8 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Junior Professor Solution: When Sheldon has to teach a course at the university, Howard enrols in his class. Tension brews between Penny and Bernadette. (S8 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bad Beat: Peralta and Jeffords go undercover at an illegal gambling club to track down an arms dealer. Hitchcock and Scully have an unusual challenge for Diaz. (S5 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Venue: The Vulture makes an unwelcome return to Peralta and Santiago's lives. Boyle and Diaz must track down kidnapped NYPD horse Sergeant Peanut Butter. (S5 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: How I Wet Your Mother: Homer develops a bedwetting habit, so the family infiltrate his dreams and search for clues in his subconscious to find the source of his problem. (S23 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Them, Robot: Mr Burns replaces the power plant's staff with robots but decides to keep Homer as the only human employee. (S23 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At the first Commitment Ceremony, some couples celebrate their success so far. But as two couples clash, one bride's bad-mouthing lands her in hot water. (S10 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rude(ish) Tube Shorts
E4Plus1.uk.description: Cheeky clips from Rude Tube's naughty little sister Rude(ish) Tube, featuring weddings, space and sci-fi fans.

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Strong Arms of the Ma: When Marge is mugged, she reacts by working out with weights, but goes too far and ends up as a steroid-crazed bully. (S14 Ep9/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pray Anything: Jealous of Flanders' lifestyle, Homer starts to pray for material possessions, but things get out of hand when he asks for a bigger house and gets the church. (S14 Ep10/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Clare sets out for revenge, while the walls close in on Jez. And a resident is determined to end their family's reign of destruction.

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Hollyoaks Unwrapped
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Expect set secrets, gossip, interviews and more, as Kieron Richardson unwraps the world of Hollyoaks, with Anna Passey, Natalie Casey, Nick Pickard and Tamara Wall. (Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Louis, a male escort who's hairless from the neck down, meets Essex-born cleaning fanatic Fleur. Eccentric gas-fitter-come-art-gallerist Ian wants someone who'll love his quirks. (S19 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's Experts Week, and time for our newly-weds to strengthen their marriages. And it's married at first spice for some, thanks to Charlene's intimacy workshop! (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Amanda is looking for a husband, and Chris hopes to overcome his geeky stereotype. Meanwhile, more than 1000 men have applied to date cheerleading coach Fayhe from episode one. (S1 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sian, who's 24, wants a man to drive her wild, who she can love more than her beloved car. And 33-year-old fashion entrepreneur Tansel is after a woman to settle down with. (S8 Ep5/5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the box this time, SAS: Who Dares Wins, Dragons' Den, Three Families, Headspace: Guide to Sleep, Secret Crush, Lego Masters USA, This Morning and BBC News (holidays). (S17 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's Experts Week, and time for our newly-weds to strengthen their marriages. And it's married at first spice for some, thanks to Charlene's intimacy workshop! (S10 Ep9) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Below Deck
E4Plus1.uk.description: Happy Captain, Happy Life: A new crew member is thrown in at the deep end. Barbie and Kyle struggle after taking their relationship to the next level. (S11 Ep13/17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Helter Skelter: The Simpsons' house must be fumigated after a hockey player gives Lisa his termite-infested stick. The only place they can find to live is in a reality TV show. (S14 Ep5/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Great Louse Detective: When someone tries to murder Homer, Chief Wiggum seeks help from someone who understands the mind of a killer: Sideshow Bob. (S14 Ep6/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Fortification Implementation: When Sheldon and Amy build a blanket fort, they come to a major crossroads in their relationship. Howard meets his half-brother. (S8 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Communication Deterioration: Raj is asked to create a message for NASA to use if one of their missions finds alien life. Penny considers taking up acting again. (S8 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Graduation Transmission: Leonard is invited to make a speech at his old high school. Howard and Sheldon can't make a toy drone fly. (S8 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Down City: Gordon Ramsay tries to save struggling restaurant Down City in Providence, Rhode Island. But tough-talking owner Abby refuses to take advice from anyone. (S4 Ep3) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Weathering Heights: Phil's excited when he's invited onto the local news. And his day gets even better when he meets his weatherman hero, Rainer Shine (guest star Nathan Fillion). (S8 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Halloween 4: The Revenge of Rod Skyhook: Luke's Halloween party isn't going well. The Dunphys decide it needs a visit from Rod Skyhook, some promotion and adult supervision... (S8 Ep5)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: There once was an Irish pub, named after a big green bug. It was on its last legs, down to the dregs. Welcome to Ramsay's Nightmare club! #NationalPoetryDay [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's time to get intimate and go deep, for some it's awks, others a big leap. Time to lay it bare, nothing to hide, but interference makes some pairs collide. #NationalPoetryDay (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge and Lisa debate a feminist ideal. Beauty, brains AND power: illusion or real? Can those three things be combined? Seeking insight from history, what do they find? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: When a nearby economy is all out of luck, men head to Springfield looking for work. An honest day's work for an honest day's pay? Not if Mayor Quimby can keep them away. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Due to his terrible self-worth, Raj vows to give women a wide berth. Penny tries to teach Sheldon - which is no easy feat. We hope you enjoy this Big Bang repeat. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Leonard, Sheldon and Howard talk science. Will they be met with some defiance? Raj plans a date to help Lucy's fears; let's hope this one won't end in tears. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: When Phil and Claire are caught in bed, their kids are filled with nothing but dread. Jay and Gloria send an email, but to the wrong person. Epic fail! #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: To make sure they don't become boring, Claire and Phil have new bed plans that don't involve snoring. And Jay's got a surprise in store, but executing it becomes a chore. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Howard hurls the first pitch at a baseball game, but will his throw just bring him shame? And Sheldon makes a hefty remark; Penny and Leonard think he's missed the mark. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will the guys invest in Stuart's shop; or will their girlfriends throw a strop? From Penny, Emily keeps her distance; how long can she ignore her existence? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Penny's accused of spoiling the fun, but she's got to get her revision done. The guys try to invent something that's new, but nothing they do leads to a breakthrough. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sheldon and Raj test if they'd cope in a mine. Will they both make it out fine? Penny and Leonard worry about cash, as Penny's gesture meets a backlash. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Captain Holt has had his pie taken. It's enough to leave anyone shaken. Track it down he must. The filling and crust. But who did this dastardly break-in? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jeffords, Peralta and Diaz have a mission, to find out who stole Parlov's fiction. The rest of the squad take a forensics programme; but Boyle's mouth lands him in a jam. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Simpsons don't want to leave their cruise, so Bart comes up with a clever ruse. He starts pretending, that the world is ending. Oh no, what terrible news... #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: With the help of a rather dashing, crime-fighting spy, can Homer be a better husband? Well, he'll give it a try... #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's time to get intimate and go deep, for some it's awks, others a big leap. Time to lay it bare, nothing to hide, but interference makes some pairs collide. #NationalPoetryDay (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sheldon applies pressure for a wedding date. But Penny and Leonard want to wait. Raj has a wobble. Will it lead to a squabble? All as Amy re-evaluates. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: A confession leaves Penny in shock, as Leonard says he's run amok. And Sheldon feels utter heartache, when Amy puts their relationship on a break. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart learns he made loads of cash as a baby ad star, but much to his frustration; it turns out Homer's spent it all, so Bart files for emancipation. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer tours the country on the trail of a special burger. Lisa joins a spelling bee but the competition's murder. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: What unlikely events lead to Lisa going undercover as a nun? I think it's something to do with Marge looking straight at the sun. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Krusty'll never know if his dead dad approves of his legacy. Lisa's very worried about Homer's life expectancy. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates: Valentine's
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will twins find blokes with va va voom, in our so-romantic dining room?  And can Roisin from Ireland bring a love thang, for bar manager Saskia who loves a Gaelic twang? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: The dinner party serves up romantic confessions, with a side order of tricky questions. Can a bride get her validation, or will it be a red flag illumination? #NationalPoetryDay (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: A cosy throwback to 2021, for some Gogglebox moments, but what was on? Can't remember? Leave it to our critics, to see what they think about telly's best picks. #NationalPoetryDay

Film4.uk.title: Dead Man's Shoes
Film4.uk.description: (2004) Shane Meadows' thriller starring Paddy Considine, Gary Stretch and Toby Kebbell. An ex-soldier is bent on revenge against the drug dealers who cruelly tormented his younger brother.

Film4.uk.title: Joyland
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Poignant familial drama about the pressures felt by those who don't slot neatly into the mores of Pakistan's strictly patriarchal, judgemental society. In Urdu, Punjabi/subs.

Film4.uk.title: The Remains of the Day
Film4.uk.description: (1993) Anthony Hopkins stars in this subtle drama about the dedicated butler of a post-WWI home whose loyalties are tested when the housekeeper (Emma Thompson) falls in love with him.

Film4.uk.title: A Lawless Street
Film4.uk.description: (1955) A non-stop romp of a western from director Joseph H Lewis. In the town of Medicine Bend, only Marshal Calem Ware can keep its citizens from falling into complete lawlessness.

Film4.uk.title: The Blue Lamp
Film4.uk.description: (1950) Gritty noir thriller from Ealing Studios. A rookie PC hunts a vicious killer across blitz-battered London. With Jimmy Hanley, Dirk Bogarde and Jack Warner as PC George Dixon.

Film4.uk.title: Anastasia
Film4.uk.description: (1956) Historical drama. The Oscar-winning Ingrid Bergman stars as an amnesiac refugee who Yul Brynner tries to pass off as the daughter of the murdered Tsar of Russia, Nicholas II.

Film4.uk.title: The Old Man and the Gun
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Crime biopic. Robert Redford stars as charming 74-year-old robber Forrest Tucker. He's still robbing banks when he falls for farmer Jewel (Sissy Spacek). But the cops still want him.

Film4.uk.title: Tombstone
Film4.uk.description: (1993) Western. Kurt Russell stars in the story of legendary Wild West lawman Wyatt Earp told through the medium of the moustache. With Val Kilmer as 'Doc' Holliday and Charlton Heston.

Film4.uk.title: On the Come Up
Film4.uk.description: (2022) Jamila Gray stars as Lil' Law'- a struggling young rapper who wants to make her fortune to help her family in director Sanaa Lathan's hip-hop-battling-coming-of-fame drama.

Film4.uk.title: Climax
Film4.uk.description: (2018) Hallucinogenic thriller. Dancers gather in a deserted building. But the sangria's spiked. In French/subs.

More4Plus1.uk.title: Four in a Bed

More4Plus1.uk.title: Car S.O.S

More4Plus1.uk.title: Location, Location, Location

More4Plus1.uk.title: Location, Location, Location

More4Plus1.uk.title: Grand Designs
